flegt men kayklen di eyer. s'iz geven a bretl un me flegt aropkayklen, un azoy iz geven mit nislekh.

00:13:53.042 --> 00:13:56.195
flegt men zogn, az me flegt nemen in hant a nisl,

00:13:56.269 --> 00:14:00.684
un me flegt darfn trefn velkhe hant: "rekhts, links, rekhts, links."

00:14:02.513 --> 00:14:04.532
me flegt shpiln in kneplekh.

00:14:05.095 --> 00:14:06.304
un vi?

00:14:06.445 --> 00:14:08.177
m'hot gegebn a hak in vant,

00:14:08.453 --> 00:14:11.310
un er flegt opshpringen. s'flegt zayn a lekhl,

00:14:11.310 --> 00:14:14.302
aza arumgetsamt, un me flegt darfn araynshneln ot azoy.

00:14:15.523 --> 00:14:17.694
s'iz geven andere shpiln, nit itstike.

00:14:25.665 --> 00:14:28.848
ir hot geendikt di shul?

00:14:29.057 --> 00:14:31.982
tsu draytsn yor, un avek arbetn.

00:14:31.982 --> 00:14:34.198
dan hot zikh gerufn bar-mitsve.

00:14:34.828 --> 00:14:37.488
nokh derayn bin ikh shoyn a groyser mentsh.

00:14:37.579 --> 00:14:41.285
bin ikh avek arbetn, nit kukndik vos kh'hob nit dergreykht dem tish.

00:14:45.510 --> 00:14:48.974
vu un bay vos hot ir gearbet?

00:14:48.413 --> 00:14:51.495
ikh bin zikh avek lern-, bay shloseray.

00:14:52.075 --> 00:14:54.278
hob ikh nit dergreykht dem tish.

00:14:54.278 --> 00:14:58.566
hob ikh opgearbet a monat tsayt un gerufn di mame, ikh zol geyn in shtub.

00:14:58.909 --> 00:15:00.776
hot mir mayne a tante

00:15:01.086 --> 00:15:04.404
avekgefirt bay zikh, ikh zol zikh lernen shnayderay.

00:15:04.579 --> 00:15:07.728
dortn hob ikh gelernt, opgearbet di gantse yorn

00:15:07.853 --> 00:15:09.011
biz haynt.

00:15:12.257 --> 00:15:15.879
vi hot oysgezen di shnayderay bay di tantn?

00:15:16.455 --> 00:15:18.495
a- an alter bokher,

00:15:19.412 --> 00:15:27.177
zi hot gearbet, un ikh hob gearbet. ikh bin geven der ler-yingl, zi iz geven di arbeterke, un er hot aleyn gearbet. gelebt hot er in eyn tsimer.

00:15:27.445 --> 00:15:29.633
ver iz dos geven, der arbeter?

00:15:29.233 --> 00:15:31.690
der balebos iz geven Berl Khaytin.

00:15:30.162 --> 00:15:31.067
UNK

00:15:38.397 --> 00:15:42.221
a! gearbet hob ikh oyf Nemuno akhtsn.

00:15:55.845 --> 00:16:01.458
nokh tsvey yor arbetn bin ikh ave-, dortn hob ikh geneyt hoyzn un vest.

00:16:01.667 --> 00:16:06.979
nokh tsvey arbet, tsvey yor arbetn, bin ikh avekgegangen bay an ander shnayder,

00:16:06.979 --> 00:16:08.951
oyf Grodner dray.

00:16:10.729 --> 00:16:12.478
hob ikh gearbet

00:16:13.581 --> 00:16:15.667
biz di rusn zaynen arayn.

00:16:20.702 --> 00:16:22.147
dernokh bin ikh...

00:16:21.698 --> 00:16:26.332
vi iz geven ayer ekonomishe lage, ir hot shoyn ongehoybn arbetn?

00:16:25.950 --> 00:16:28.087
geven a bisl laykhter,

00:16:28.566 --> 00:16:32.930
vayle der, di gelt fleg ikh opgebn di tatn un mamen.

00:16:35.248 --> 00:16:40.029
un an erekh vifl hot men aykh getsolt far ayer sh⟨uleray⟩?

00:16:39.180 --> 00:16:44.776
dray monat hob ikh gearbet on gelt, nor der balebos oyf kino flegt mir gebn ale fraytik.

00:16:44.985 --> 00:16:48.691
nokh dray monat hot men mir genumen tsoln draysik lit a khoydesh.

00:16:48.867 --> 00:16:50.312
s'iz geven a sakh gelt.

00:16:51.128 --> 00:16:53.366
fleg ikh avekgebn biz a tsent.

00:16:54.030 --> 00:16:56.176
un az ikh fleg blaybn a mol,

00:16:56.176 --> 00:17:00.875
bay dem ershtn balebos, flegt er m-, merer shoyn arbetn,

00:17:00.983 --> 00:17:04.132
⟨i-⟩ di gelt fleg ikh nem- flegt men mir avekgebn.

00:17:04.132 --> 00:17:06.250
nor di, di ZA-, di gelt

00:17:06.250 --> 00:17:09.641
vos ikh fleg fardinen dem khoydesh fleg ikh opgebn tate-mamen.

00:17:09.641 --> 00:17:10.881
s'iz geven an ander,

00:17:10.881 --> 00:17:12.298
andersh vi itster.

00:17:13.690 --> 00:17:16.974
nokh der arbet, mit vos hot ir zikh farnumen?

00:17:16.693 --> 00:17:20.349
⟨m'iz⟩, nokh der arbet flegt men zikh oykh shpiln, kinder,

00:17:20.963 --> 00:17:26.171
mit a futbol. ⟨ikh, nu,⟩ geshpilt zikh vi kinder. zamd, ikh veys,

00:17:26.515 --> 00:17:28.956
vayl der hoyf iz geven a zamdiker.

00:17:30.784 --> 00:17:34.453
un vi hot oysgezen di gas vu ir hot gelebt?

00:17:34.767 --> 00:17:39.401
di gas iz geven a ⟨g-⟩ a fayne gas, geven Ukmerge plente,

00:17:40.015 --> 00:17:43.755
un, antkegn iz geven a mark, in yener tsayt.

00:17:44.689 --> 00:17:46.407
s⟨'iz op⟩geboyt a,

00:17:46.407 --> 00:17:47.791
a koshtshol,

00:17:47.791 --> 00:17:50.944
a zeyer a groyser, a royter. er shteyt itster oykh.

00:17:51.473 --> 00:17:54.412
nu, mir flegn kukn in di fentster, vi ale kinder,

00:17:54.412 --> 00:17:58.537
shpiln in di kartinkelekh. flegt men ⟨nemen⟩ fun a konfetke, oyfdreyen,

00:17:58.780 --> 00:18:01.879
un me flegt dos shneln. andere shpiln iz geven vi itster.

00:18:03.589 --> 00:18:05.878
keyn tsatskes hobn mir nit gehat.

00:18:08.567 --> 00:18:14.248
ir hot gefilt velkhe nit iz batsiungen tsvishn yidn un kristn?

00:18:13.815 --> 00:18:15.648
yener tsayt nit.

00:18:16.279 --> 00:18:18.298
gelebt hot men vi brider.

00:18:22.303 --> 00:18:28.962
un vu flegt ir, ⟨⟩, mit zey, kristn, vu flegt ir mit zey hobn kontaktn?

00:18:29.053 --> 00:18:32.253
⟨, zey⟩ hobn dokh gelebt tsuzamen mit undz in di hoyfn.

00:18:33.306 --> 00:18:35.999
flegt men zikh mit oykh z- mit zey oykh shpiln.

00:18:35.999 --> 00:18:37.680
lernen, farshteyt zikh, hobn,

00:18:37.680 --> 00:18:40.639
hobn mir gelernt yidish un zey hobn gelernt litvish.

00:18:43.667 --> 00:18:47.795
un az s'flegt zayn yontoyvim kristlekhe?

00:18:48.679 --> 00:18:55.524
kristlekhe yontoyvim, i- mir zaynen nit geven, tsuge- vayle ze- zeyer esn hobn mir dokh nit getort esn.

00:18:55.750 --> 00:19:02.052
nu, es flegt zayn undzere yontoyvim, peysekh, nokh azelkhe, flegn mir zey arayntrogn vayn. me flegt dan makhn

00:19:02.052 --> 00:19:03.489
bay yidn med.

00:19:04.035 --> 00:19:07.016
flegt men zey arayntrogn, a fleshl med,

00:19:07.343 --> 00:19:11.184
u- un gegebn zey matse, zey hobn gehat holt.

00:19:14.177 --> 00:19:19.436
di kloyz in Kovne vu ir hot gegangen, kent ir zikh dermonen?

00:19:18.042 --> 00:19:23.571
ye. di ko- di kloyz iz geven, hinter undz azoy, ⟨ot⟩ di tsveyte gas,

00:19:24.201 --> 00:19:25.798
 V⟨UNK⟩⟨she⟩ gas.

00:19:29.128 --> 00:19:31.214
derbay iz geven a bekeray

00:19:31.727 --> 00:19:33.780
vu me fleg koyfn broyt.

00:19:35.777 --> 00:19:37.273
di kloyz shteyt;

00:19:37.870 --> 00:19:40.277
far m- nokh di milkhome iz zi geven.

00:19:40.603 --> 00:19:43.426
undzer hoyz hot men aropgenumen itst.

00:19:43.426 --> 00:19:45.744
s'iz gevorn a sheyne, fayne gas.

00:19:46.375 --> 00:19:48.782
a gantse rey hayzer ⟨m- hot men⟩ aropgenumen

00:19:48.807 --> 00:19:51.223
UNK ⟨a ts- az-⟩

00:19:51.223 --> 00:19:53.607
akht, tsen hayzer, oybe nit merer.

00:19:54.913 --> 00:19:56.695
un itster iz dortn aza,

00:19:57.411 --> 00:19:58.890
a shpatsir gas.

00:20:01.360 --> 00:20:04.774
dem mark vos iz geven antkegn undzer shtub hot men aribergefirt

00:20:04.774 --> 00:20:06.315
vayter oyf...

00:20:07.890 --> 00:20:11.807
gedenk ikh nit. vu dos iz veys ikh, ober kh'gedenk nit.

00:20:12.396 --> 00:20:14.229
dos darf ikh zikh dermonen.

00:20:17.678 --> 00:20:20.794
oyfn mark, vos flegt men farkoyfn?

00:20:21.053 --> 00:20:23.882
farkoyfn altsding: esn...

00:20:23.888 --> 00:20:25.198
in Lite

00:20:25.440 --> 00:20:26.936
iz geven

00:20:27.027 --> 00:20:31.596
altsding vos ⟨ir kent⟩ nor visn: i puter, i eyer, i fleysh, i...

00:20:31.596 --> 00:20:36.153
vos ir vilt: i fish, i ⟨stri⟩melekh. Lite hot gehat esn

00:20:36.153 --> 00:20:37.399
bizn haldz.

00:20:39.058 --> 00:20:41.026
esn iz geven zeyer fil.

00:20:41.269 --> 00:20:43.315
Lite iz geven raykh

00:20:43.315 --> 00:20:44.452
in esn.

00:20:44.492 --> 00:20:46.902
un der gantser handl in Lite

00:20:46.902 --> 00:20:49.127
iz geven nor esn.

00:20:49.217 --> 00:20:51.759
di eyntsike zakh vos Lite hot gehat fun,

00:20:51.833 --> 00:20:55.809
fun UNK iz geven nor makhn tsvekes in Shants.

00:20:58.718 --> 00:21:00.197
nor esn...

00:21:02.025 --> 00:21:04.584
me flegt arayngeyn bay a Litviner,

00:21:04.911 --> 00:21:06.519
flegt er ale mol

00:21:06.519 --> 00:21:07.825
forleygn

00:21:07.999 --> 00:21:10.052
broyt, puter, kez.

00:21:16.234 --> 00:21:20.379
un vi... koyfn hobn dos ale gekent?

00:21:19.879 --> 00:21:20.801
neyn.

00:21:22.258 --> 00:21:24.894
oreme hobn gekoyft ergere.

00:21:24.894 --> 00:21:28.833
nu, m'hot gekoyft, vi z- dorfishe puter iz geven biliker,

00:21:29.295 --> 00:21:31.950
un s'flegt do⟨kh⟩ zayn beser vi shtotishe.

00:21:31.950 --> 00:21:33.802
nu, ver s'hot gekent hot ge-

00:21:33.802 --> 00:21:37.068
hot gekoyft a groyse; ver s'hot gekoyft, hot gekent a kleyne.

00:21:37.068 --> 00:21:39.364
tsum bayshpil, bay undz: epl.

00:21:39.437 --> 00:21:41.743
flegt der foter koyfn a zak.

00:21:42.255 --> 00:21:45.289
me flegt avekshteln vayl di kinder zoln esn,

00:21:45.289 --> 00:21:48.020
nor nit heysn tsebaysn un avekvarfn.

00:21:52.498 --> 00:21:55.051
⟨nu, azoy,⟩ m'hot gegesn, m'hot gegesn, ⟨⟩...

00:21:55.051 --> 00:21:57.454
fleg koyfn a khale mit milkh,

00:21:57.454 --> 00:22:00.356
me fleg broyt mit marmelad esn.

00:22:02.218 --> 00:22:03.916
ot dos iz geven di esn.

00:22:04.513 --> 00:22:07.443
⟨fleg⟩ opkokhn bulbe un koyfn a hering

00:22:07.838 --> 00:22:09.688
mit zoyere kroyt.

00:22:11.922 --> 00:22:17.434
un in tsayt fun di yo- yontoyvim yidishe, iz geven velkhe nit iz spetsyele?

00:22:15.988 --> 00:22:18.142
flegt men beser gebn esn.

00:22:18.520 --> 00:22:20.297
fleg men oysmakhn,

00:22:20.297 --> 00:22:23.947
flegt men makhn a kugl, a tsholnt, hot zikh dos dan gerufn.

00:22:24.156 --> 00:22:26.311
nu, m'hot azoy ge- gelebt.

00:22:26.316 --> 00:22:30.039
un a mol flegt feln gelt, flegt men layen bay

00:22:30.282 --> 00:22:31.693
farmeglekhe,

00:22:32.037 --> 00:22:35.811
un m'flegt makhn, me zol hobn a gutn shabes oder a gutn yontev.

00:22:41.959 --> 00:22:45.564
ir kent zikh dermonen dem tog az s'iz gekumen

00:22:46.903 --> 00:22:48.805
di rusishe makht,

00:22:48.912 --> 00:22:50.636
di sovetishe makht?

00:22:49.435 --> 00:22:52.532
in fertsiktn tsu in, eyn un...?

00:22:52.064 --> 00:22:53.935
in fertsikstn.

00:22:53.451 --> 00:22:58.423
fertsiktn yor iz gekumen di rusishe makht. farshteyt zikh, s'iz alts geb⟨UNK⟩- ⟨ge-⟩

00:22:58.446 --> 00:23:00.583
oyfgenumen hot men zey gut.

00:23:01.652 --> 00:23:03.350
oyfgenumen gut,

00:23:01.687 --> 00:23:03.272
efsher k-...

00:23:03.424 --> 00:23:09.088
nor tsi- tsay- in a vokh tsayt iz gevorn ale produktn oyf tsen mol merer,

00:23:09.263 --> 00:23:10.571
tayerer,

00:23:11.997 --> 00:23:14.045
un m'hot genumen khapn,

00:23:14.045 --> 00:23:17.508
vayle m'hot gemeynt, bay di rusn vet zayn hunger.

00:23:18.325 --> 00:23:20.458
azoy iz geven bay undz oykh.

00:23:21.868 --> 00:23:25.223
ver s'hot gekent, ver s'hot gekhapt mer, ver s'hot gekhapt teyl,

00:23:25.223 --> 00:23:25.898
v-

00:23:25.898 --> 00:23:29.169
vayle m'hot gemeynt, m'hot ge- gevust az dortn iz

00:23:31.453 --> 00:23:32.763
alts farsheydn.

00:23:34.170 --> 00:23:36.594
efsher gedenkt ir dem tog

00:23:37.663 --> 00:23:39.844
ven s'hot gebitn di makht?

00:23:39.844 --> 00:23:42.314
efsher etlekhe teg far dos?

00:23:42.388 --> 00:23:44.621
⟨h⟩ot, vos hot ir gezen in shtot?

00:23:44.621 --> 00:23:47.529
efsher vegn vos hot men geredt in shtub?

00:23:44.886 --> 00:23:48.862
in shtot hot men, in shtot hot men zeyer gut ge-

00:23:48.919 --> 00:23:49.996
g-, nu,

00:23:49.996 --> 00:23:51.506
g- getrofn.

00:23:51.506 --> 00:23:55.072
m'hot gepatsht mit di hent. alts iz geven rikhtik.

00:23:55.163 --> 00:23:59.409
nor m'hot gezen di rusishe armey, vi zi iz arayn mit di kleyne ferdelekh,

00:23:59.466 --> 00:24:03.976
shmutsike. dos iz geven shreklekh. zey zaynen geforn mistome a zekhtsik, zibetsik kilometer.

00:24:03.976 --> 00:24:05.457
s'iz geven shreklekh tsu kukn.

00:24:05.457 --> 00:24:06.732
nor m'hot gegleybt.

00:24:06.823 --> 00:24:09.466
me gleybt in got, hot men gegleybt in zey.

00:24:12.763 --> 00:24:16.166
oyf ayer arbetsort, hot zikh vos nit iz gebitn?

00:24:16.206 --> 00:24:17.246
 ye.

00:24:18.298 --> 00:24:20.941
nu, s'iz gevorn glaykh arteln.

00:24:21.471 --> 00:24:24.401
fun di balebatim hot men tsugenumen di mashines.

00:24:25.302 --> 00:24:27.962
un di arteln iz geven azoy:

00:24:28.137 --> 00:24:29.481
m'hot tseshlept,

00:24:30.043 --> 00:24:32.557
di etsem balebatim hobn tseshlept...

00:24:32.557 --> 00:24:34.762
zey hobn gedarft opgebn di zakazn

00:24:35.207 --> 00:24:41.529
di klyentn. hobn zey, hobn zey di, geshikt di klyentn, zey zoln tsunemen di zakazn, iz nit geven keyn arbet.

00:24:41.603 --> 00:24:44.060
un me flegt a bisl ganvenen.

00:24:44.556 --> 00:24:49.744
hot men genumen sudeven. hot men gezogt az me vet dokh undz araynzetsn nokhn zak-

00:24:49.744 --> 00:24:51.772
nokh di rusishe zakones.

00:24:51.930 --> 00:24:56.767
hot mir der foter gezogt, "gey avek fun der arbet. darfst dokh alts eyns geyn in armey."

00:24:56.993 --> 00:24:58.472
bin ikh geven in shtub.

00:24:58.731 --> 00:25:02.077
nu, ikh fleg onnemen dortn, ⟨vemen⟩ UNK dan hot men ge-

00:25:02.077 --> 00:25:05.154
umgekert kostyumen oyf der anderer zayt, s'zol zayn nayer.

00:25:05.565 --> 00:25:10.334
fleg ikh yeder sh- onnemen an altn kostyum, ⟨UNK⟩n eyn⟨e⟩ a por hoyzn, ⟨un⟩ altsding.

00:25:10.341 --> 00:25:12.224
dos iz geven mayn arbet.

00:25:12.940 --> 00:25:14.776
un di rusn zaynen arayn UNK,

00:25:14.776 --> 00:25:16.494
⟨⟩, di daytshn zaynen arayn.

00:25:17.023 --> 00:25:17.793
UNK...

00:25:17.698 --> 00:25:19.224
 i- ir

00:25:19.224 --> 00:25:23.323
efsher dermont zikh nokh dervayle merer vegn di rusishe

00:25:23.323 --> 00:25:25.976
makht in fertsikstn yor?

00:25:25.242 --> 00:25:27.058
ya. di rusishe...

00:25:25.976 --> 00:25:31.125
un di shtot hot zikh gebitn tsu nit gebitn? di mentshn? di shkheynes?

00:25:28.515 --> 00:25:30.621
keyn zakh, neyn, di,

00:25:30.621 --> 00:25:34.314
keyn zakh nit gebitn. s'iz nor gevorn alts tayerer.

00:25:34.540 --> 00:25:39.343
nu, zey hobn, farshteyt zikh, di rusn hobn gegebn films on gelt oyf di vent,

00:25:39.349 --> 00:25:41.539
in di par- in di SADn.

00:25:41.539 --> 00:25:45.379
f- me fleg zingen, makhn ta- tents

00:25:45.379 --> 00:25:48.416
far di... dan iz geven freylekh, hobn nit gevust vos

00:25:48.416 --> 00:25:49.906
dortn tut zikh.

00:25:50.436 --> 00:25:53.889
velkhe films hot men aykh bavizn, efsher gedenkt ir?

00:25:53.811 --> 00:25:56.606
⟨me fleg,⟩ vayzn "TRI TANKISTY,"

00:25:59.548 --> 00:26:02.225
"CHAPAEV," iz geven film,

00:26:03.733 --> 00:26:08.553
 vi hot zikh geruf-...? ikh veys nit vi UNK "VESЁLe REBYAT."

00:26:16.879 --> 00:26:18.307
un "Kolkhozn."

00:26:22.937 --> 00:26:26.171
un di yugnt, vi hot dos alts ongenumen?

00:26:26.160 --> 00:26:30.440
m'iz geven zeyer blind, un me, un m'hot ongenumen zeyer gut.

00:26:33.045 --> 00:26:36.811
un men hot gevust vos es tut zikh oyf der velt,

00:26:36.811 --> 00:26:39.367
in EVROPe in ot o di tsayt?

00:26:38.327 --> 00:26:40.312
keyn, keyn zakh nit.

00:26:40.403 --> 00:26:42.475
k- key- m'hot gevust,

00:26:42.475 --> 00:26:45.934
m'hot gevust az der daytsh klaybt zikh ontsufaln oyf Rusland,

00:26:45.934 --> 00:26:47.900
nor Rusland hot geleyknt.

00:26:47.900 --> 00:26:50.103
m'hot gemeynt az Rusland, dos iz

00:26:50.103 --> 00:26:50.960
got.

00:26:54.628 --> 00:26:58.773
bay aykh in shtub hot men geredt vos nit iz vegn dos?

00:26:57.767 --> 00:27:01.652
neyn, keyn politik hot men nit geredt. geredt nor vegn shtu-

00:27:01.652 --> 00:27:03.178
mir hobn gehat eygene UNK...

00:27:04.028 --> 00:27:05.119
khayune.

00:27:12.263 --> 00:27:16.003
avelkhe shprakh hot men dan geredt in Kovne?

00:27:14.507 --> 00:27:17.353
yidi- yidish. yidish, litvish.

00:27:18.658 --> 00:27:20.694
keyn rusish hot men nit geredt.

00:27:21.696 --> 00:27:26.510
nor ir hot nokh gekent reydn yidish oyf di gasn?

00:27:25.358 --> 00:27:26.567
ye, ye.

00:27:26.510 --> 00:27:28.844
ir hot gornisht nit gefilt?

00:27:27.788 --> 00:27:29.385
keyn zakh nit.

00:27:31.872 --> 00:27:33.671
keyn zakh nit. geredt...

00:27:35.348 --> 00:27:37.721
un in kloyz hot ir gegangen,

00:27:38.098 --> 00:27:39.290
shabes...

00:27:38.183 --> 00:27:40.640
shoyn in di rusishe tsaytn?

00:27:40.697 --> 00:27:43.475
di rusishe tsaytn, shabes flegt men geyn.

00:27:46.266 --> 00:27:52.637
un, men hot gornisht nit gefilt, oyf di kloyz iz nit geven keyn, drikungen fun, fun di makht?

00:27:50.974 --> 00:27:53.178
dem, dem ershtn yor, neyn.

00:27:55.615 --> 00:27:57.954
g- gefilt hot men ven zey zaynen gekumen

00:27:58.315 --> 00:27:59.811
a tsveyt mol.

00:28:09.469 --> 00:28:11.471
nu, dan vayter.

00:28:13.232 --> 00:28:14.289
vayter?

00:28:14.582 --> 00:28:16.753
onfangen vegn di milkhome?

00:28:16.624 --> 00:28:22.676
ot dem ershtn tog, vi hot ir zikh dervust az di milkhome iz ongefangen?

00:28:22.311 --> 00:28:25.269
ikh bin dan geforn fun Kovne

00:28:25.269 --> 00:28:26.861
in Valakumpe...

00:28:27.137 --> 00:28:29.780
iz do a forshtot, a datshne shtot...

00:28:30.951 --> 00:28:33.544
un az ikh bin aroyf oyfn parakhod,

00:28:33.668 --> 00:28:34.640
oyf di,

00:28:35.434 --> 00:28:39.058
oy- oyf di shi-, vi ruft ⟨men⟩... parakhod?

00:28:39.051 --> 00:28:40.297
oyfn shif.

00:28:39.810 --> 00:28:42.133
ye, iz gevorn a sirene

00:28:43.219 --> 00:28:44.850
fun di daytshn.

00:28:44.890 --> 00:28:47.145
s'iz geven akht a zeyger in der fri.

00:28:49.682 --> 00:28:52.159
un m'hot genumen loyfn in Rusland.

00:28:52.159 --> 00:28:53.914
ver, vu, s'iz gevorn

00:28:53.914 --> 00:28:55.396
der tuml groys.

00:28:56.736 --> 00:28:57.560
baym...
